{"tid":793172,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"巴絲幾耐會痾一次屎?_?","createTime":"2018-08-25T07:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T07:23:52.000Z","uid":126875,"like":177,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"f2964d159e4d6acd9bcb1fa1bdaad04d1ff083bb","tid":793172,"uid":126875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T07:19:47.000Z","msg":"我由細到大都好少屎痾，細細個唔知正常應該係日日都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  到大啲先知原來無屎痾係有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  自有記憶以嚟，都係5-7日先有一篤，唔係就係肚痛先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試過差唔多兩個禮拜都無去過大，應該係有太多屎喺入面搞到肚痛先有得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日覺得自己係會生大腸癌死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴絲可以解答下究竟點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：差唔多日日一篤 唔痾唔知身體好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：無得痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 飲奶食蕉食奇異果都係無得痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但好彩無生過痔瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d88098620f9e1e9fb70554b2182e8ab045032fdd","tid":793172,"uid":185377,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T07:25:31.000Z","msg":"我都平均1.5日先有一次= =<br />\n唔係日日都痾"},{"pid":"131e16a4b314a917f622e2fe24b809d67b047641","tid":793172,"uid":190258,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T07:48:32.000Z","msg":"一日至少三次"},{"pid":"3f950f6ca730491c9b8533f44b813a9a20746fce","tid":793172,"uid":170044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T07:49:53.000Z","msg":"我平時一星期1-2次 極少有便意"},{"pid":"99a781da9f3d170c6e6587ae1b19e99be3eaa56a","tid":793172,"uid":197852,"like":3,"dis