me":"2018-08-25T07:55:30.000Z","msg":"樓主食野多唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果食野多都冇得痾就好大獲"},{"pid":"886cd0c42009bd50c463d544b98d07cda5f8afa8","tid":793172,"uid":93350,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T07:57:27.000Z","msg":"樓主消化得好好 咩都比你吸哂入身體入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f972653bf00f949565af7509383cba0761881085","tid":793172,"uid":74685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T07:58:25.000Z","msg":"一日三次同三日一次都係正常（好似係），主要係睇習慣<br />\n如果無啦啦突然變咗，即係可能有啲唔妥<br />\n<br />\n但樓豬5-7日一次又真係耐咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試下改變日常飲食，食得健康啲<br />\n同埋建立下屙屎習慣，固定搵個時間坐喺屎塔"},{"pid":"681c9c32ba8ac45b7901d015aa59ad0500d49050","tid":793172,"uid":126875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5da890d5dd8e943138ab426738cfb3d636fe750","tid":793172,"uid":24470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2c80895c33bb8de1c896817136f177a995f91437","tid":793172,"uid":126875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6e7271b901523886dfd5145f17033d9eb02c78bb","tid":793172,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T07:52:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T07:53:52.000Z","msg":"我啲屎係鴨屎綠色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T07:55:16.000Z","msg":"睇下醫生好喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T07:59:02.000Z","msg":"睇過一個中醫佢話有得痾就痾 無得痾即係吸收晒唔需要痾 我仲生存到即係無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇西醫叫我驗屎 驗完話無見到有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6a2e329839c2d7309f1e4bb9fed2e4aedde046","tid":793172,"uid":126875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b68c27d238098d27a3af505aebd07af9c6849186","tid":793172,"uid":76253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep